comments:
Build a static library in a separate sub-process.

Parameters ---------- objects : list or tuple of str List of paths to object files used to build the static library. output_libname : str The library name as an absolute or relative (if `output_dir` is used) path. output_dir : str, optional The path to the output directory. Default is None, in which case the ``output_dir`` attribute of the UnixCCompiler instance. debug : bool, optional This parameter is not used. target_lang : str, optional This parameter is not used.
##### Returns
